    <h1 class="headline">Five Days to the Deadline: Markets Are Not Ready for April 6</h1>

    <p class="deck">
      The S&amp;P 500 closed Q1 on uncertain footing, oil is hovering in territory that rewrites inflation math, and the Federal Reserve has all but told markets not to expect relief. Whatever happens at Hormuz in the next five days will define the second quarter.
    </p>

